        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix(feishu): parse all merge-forward sub-messages and extract interactive card text",
        "body": "## Summary\n\nWhen a Feishu merge_forward message contains interactive/card sub-messages (tables, cards), they were either silently dropped or rendered as bare `[interactive]` text. Two fixes:\n\n1. **Filter fix**: `parseMergeForwardContent` only included items with `upper_message_id`, dropping interactive sub-messages that don't have this field. Changed to include all items except the root merge_forward container.\n\n2. **Content extraction**: `formatSubMessageContent` returned bare `[interactive]` for any unrecognized content type. Added `extractInteractiveText()` that parses Feishu card JSON to extract title/element text.\n\nFixes #77909\n\n## Tests and validation\n\n```bash\n$ node scripts/run-vitest.mjs extensions/feishu/src/bot.test.ts\n Test Files  1 passed (1)\n      Tests  87 passed (87)\n```\n",
